rows.label: bf09320100_0010
rows.name: The one who hasn't changed is you.

rows.label: bf09320100_0020
rows.name: That's why people who tried to change were in your way.

rows.label: bf09320100_0030
rows.name: Is there any need to change?

rows.label: bf09320100_0040
rows.name: If I change, I lose everything.

rows.label: bf09320100_0060
rows.name: No one could bear such a fate!

rows.label: bf09320100_0080
rows.name:
How weak...
You are too weak...
